## [`repair-maze.py`](https://github.com/Jothin-kumar/maze-collections/blob/main/py/repair-maze.py)
`Used in Build Process`

Fixes the following files:
 - `/maze-data/easy.txt`
 - `/maze-data/medium.txt`
 - `/maze-data/hard.txt`

Changes files from
```
"--"




"--"
```
To
```
--
--
```

 - Creates the following file structure:
 ```

 /maze
 +--/easy
    +--/max.txt
    +--/1.json
    +--/2.json
    +--etc...
 +--/medium
    +--/max.txt
    +--/1.json
    +--/2.json
    +--etc...
 +--/hard
    +--/max.txt
    +--/1.json
    +--/2.json
    +--etc...
```

## [`parse_maze.py`](https://github.com/Jothin-kumar/maze-collections/blob/main/py/parse_maze.py)
